e7a0a&_nc_ohc=NXkE2WwJ-r0Q7kNvgELMB1W&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sin6-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB2MvVV0PqMAv7E_VRdBrrdQv9GS9Hdhkp5psJzrj8JQA&oe=6728B13B"}, "display_name": "Take a Leap", "keywords": ["easy", "casual", "jump", "mr", "jelly"], "long_description": "When was the last time you took a leap of faith?\n\nThis mixed reality game strips everything back to basics \u2014 no frills, no distractions. Just you, your courage, and the thrill of the jump. Whether you're playing on your stove, ceiling, window, or door, all you need is one hand or one controller to leap forward.\n\nAnd when you fail? Get back up and leap again. \n\n- Enjoy WeChat Tiao Yi Tiao (\u8df3\u4e00\u8df3) mobile game? You\u2019ll enjoy this\n- Never ending MR hyper-casual game\n- Juicy translucent jelly art style\n- Randomly generated gummy characters and colors\n- Simple hand gesture or controller interaction\n- Challenge friends to get highest score on a leaderboard\n- Move and place on any surface in your space\n- Relatable life quotes", "short_description": "When was the last time you took a leap of faith?\n\nThis mixed reality game strips everything back to basics \u2014 no frills, no distractions. Just you, your courage, and the thrill of the jump. Whether you're playing on your stove, ceiling, window, or door, all you need is one hand or one controller to leap forward.\n\nAnd when you fail? Get back up and leap again. "}]}, "developer_name": "Lost Mood", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://lostmood.notion.site/Lost-mood-data-privacy-policies-04400bffc2da4e68acdb08cf33f08eb6?pvs=74", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Lost Mood", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.tiktok.com/@lostmood.co", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1592192974313489"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genre